snippet.title: REVENGE Official Trailer [Pre-Alpha]
snippet.description:
Fight for humanity's future & GET YOUR REVENGE! 😈

REVENGE is a co-op PvE shooter where players and spectators join forces against MARA, a sentient virus invading The Everreach. Fight her digital creatures, recover powerful artifacts, and prove your skill by surviving to claim your place at the top and save the future.

Wishlist REVENGE on Epic Games:
https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/r3v3nge1-0be179

Follow us for updates:
Web: http://www.everreachlabs.io
Twitter:   https://www.x.com/_GETREVENGE_
TikTok:   https://www.tiktok.com/@_getrevenge_
Instagram:   https://www.instagram.com/_getrevenge_/
